23:52.125 --> 23:53.416
-Welcome.
-Thanks.

23:57.625 --> 23:58.875
The one on the right.

23:58.958 --> 24:01.875
This is mine.
Why are you getting three beds?

24:08.041 --> 24:09.125
Where did you find that?

24:09.208 --> 24:10.875
Guess. Under the bed.

24:10.958 --> 24:12.041
Under the bed.

24:12.125 --> 24:13.833
Pik. Look.

24:13.916 --> 24:15.708
-At the bottom.
-It's not there.

24:15.791 --> 24:18.000
It's there. You have to look for it.

24:18.083 --> 24:19.375
He's so dumb.

24:19.458 --> 24:21.125
-Who?
-You.

24:21.208 --> 24:22.458
-Me?
-Yes.

24:29.625 --> 24:32.291
So, I asked you to come here this morning

24:32.375 --> 24:34.750
because I'd like to begin this…

24:35.291 --> 24:38.958
this conversation of ours
in front of this painting.

24:39.541 --> 24:42.125
Quite simply, I'd like you to tell me,

24:42.875 --> 24:44.625
freely,

24:46.250 --> 24:47.666
what you're seeing in it.

24:51.750 --> 24:53.750
Go on. Freely.

24:54.791 --> 24:56.291
Well, Professor,

24:57.166 --> 24:59.750
I see some men beating Jesus.

25:00.416 --> 25:02.458
There are six men

25:03.125 --> 25:04.416
beating Jesus.

25:04.500 --> 25:07.041
How would you define these six men?

25:07.125 --> 25:08.500
They're persecutors.

25:09.125 --> 25:10.208
Persecutors.

25:13.291 --> 25:14.541
And who's the victim?

25:15.041 --> 25:16.208
Well, Jesus.

25:19.375 --> 25:20.375
Are you sure?

25:20.875 --> 25:23.083
It seems to me that the persecutors

25:24.416 --> 25:25.916
are victims too.

25:26.000 --> 25:28.666
Because those who hurt others

25:29.333 --> 25:30.875
hurt themselves too.

25:32.291 --> 25:33.833
-Right?
-Right.

25:35.166 --> 25:37.958
I'd add that they
are not the only perpetrators.

25:38.041 --> 25:38.958
Jesus is too.

25:39.625 --> 25:42.541
He's using their evil to rise above them.

25:43.125 --> 25:44.333
In order to be perfect.

25:46.166 --> 25:49.333
Isn't this perfection
a display of arrogance, perhaps?

25:49.416 --> 25:50.500
What are you saying?

25:50.583 --> 25:53.333
Good is perfection, and perfection is God.

25:54.208 --> 25:57.541
I believe you should start considering

25:57.625 --> 26:00.541
that perhaps the devil manifests itself

26:00.625 --> 26:03.250
when we are in the right.

26:03.333 --> 26:08.583
When we feel inebriated by our perfection.

26:08.666 --> 26:11.291
So you're saying that when we behave well,

26:11.916 --> 26:14.208
we're following the devil's suggestions.

26:15.125 --> 26:18.375
Therefore, there is no difference
between the saint and his tormentors?

26:18.458 --> 26:19.958
Of course there is.

26:20.041 --> 26:21.666
Jesus is a man too.

26:22.833 --> 26:24.416
He became a man

26:24.500 --> 26:27.458
and, as such,
he takes part in our imperfection.

26:27.541 --> 26:28.958
Because He holds inside

26:29.458 --> 26:31.416
the seeds of evil.

26:31.500 --> 26:33.875
We become men

26:33.958 --> 26:35.666
by inheriting evil.

26:35.750 --> 26:37.791
By perpetrating evil.

26:39.125 --> 26:40.666
And being victims of evil.

26:43.333 --> 26:45.041
In order to be a victim of evil,

26:46.666 --> 26:49.625
someone must surely perpetrate it.

26:51.666 --> 26:52.666
What then?

26:53.708 --> 26:55.083
You don't agree, Gioacchino?

26:55.166 --> 26:56.666
I don't know, I…

26:57.833 --> 27:00.833
I believe we become men
by doing good deeds.

27:01.750 --> 27:03.750
You seem to be saying
that we only become men

27:03.833 --> 27:05.625
by perpetrating evil. I don't…

27:07.333 --> 27:08.458
I don't understand.

27:08.541 --> 27:11.708
So, Professor Golgota's talking nonsense.

27:17.750 --> 27:19.583
Hey. All clear. Let's go.

27:20.250 --> 27:22.333
-Where are you going?
-Hurry up. Let's go.

27:22.416 --> 27:23.791
-Me?
-Yes, come on.

27:27.791 --> 27:28.625
Hi.

27:29.416 --> 27:30.416
What are you doing?

27:30.500 --> 27:33.166
We're re-enacting
the painting we saw earlier.

27:34.750 --> 27:35.833
And why am I here?

27:35.916 --> 27:37.208
You are the protagonist.

27:37.291 --> 27:38.541
-Clothes off.
-You're Jesus.

27:38.625 --> 27:39.875
-Go on.
-Do I take my shirt off?

27:39.958 --> 27:42.791
-Yes. Bare your chest, like Him.
-Get naked.

27:42.875 --> 27:43.875
