28:21.916 --> 28:23.041
Yeah, that's enough.

28:23.125 --> 28:24.458
Say you don't believe in anything.

28:25.333 --> 28:26.708
Renounce your god, you snitch!

28:27.791 --> 28:29.000
Renounce your faith.

28:29.666 --> 28:30.875
Stay still, D'Avenia.

28:30.958 --> 28:32.000
Renounce it.

28:34.375 --> 28:35.958
What the fuck are you doing?

28:39.125 --> 28:40.666
Have you lost your minds?

29:00.333 --> 29:01.958
You sinner.

29:02.041 --> 29:04.125
You like being flogged, don't you?

29:19.375 --> 29:21.541
<i>Being born male is an incurable illness.</i>

29:22.458 --> 29:24.375
That faggot deserved it.

29:25.125 --> 29:27.375
<i>You had to be ready to do</i>
<i>or suffer all sort of things</i>

29:27.458 --> 29:30.125
<i>in order to obtain</i>
<i>the approval of your peers.</i>

29:30.208 --> 29:32.750
<i>You had to prove you were strong,</i>
<i>even if you were weak.</i>

29:33.458 --> 29:35.666
<i>Every day, you had to prove</i>
<i>you were a real man.</i>

29:35.750 --> 29:39.250
<i>Then you had to start again from scratch</i>
<i>and prove it all over again.</i>

29:40.375 --> 29:43.791
<i>If you failed once,</i>
<i>you would be marked forever.</i>

29:49.416 --> 29:52.875
TOMORROW NIGHT AT 3 AM
AT THE DEVIL'S CHAIR

29:52.958 --> 29:56.208
<i>I do not like dick!</i>

29:57.541 --> 29:58.375
