-Come on!
-No!

30:52.625 --> 30:53.458
No.

30:54.583 --> 30:55.791
Come on.

30:58.000 --> 30:59.791
-Hi, girls.
-Hi.

30:59.875 --> 31:00.833
Where are you going?

31:00.916 --> 31:02.375
I'm going home. And you?

31:02.458 --> 31:04.916
Can you give us a lift?
We missed our tram.

31:05.000 --> 31:06.583
-Where?
-Montagnola.

31:07.416 --> 31:09.416
-Where's that?
-Montagnola.

31:10.291 --> 31:13.125
Do you know Grotta Perfetta Street,
on the Laurentina?

31:13.208 --> 31:14.125
Near the EUR?

31:14.208 --> 31:15.958
-I see, the EUR!
-Yes.

31:16.041 --> 31:16.916
It's quite far.

31:18.125 --> 31:18.958
Go on, then.

31:23.291 --> 31:25.916
-Can you open it?
-Oh my God.

31:26.000 --> 31:26.833
There.

31:26.916 --> 31:28.208
Sorry.

31:28.708 --> 31:30.041
It's like a spaceship!

31:32.583 --> 31:34.125
Have you seen how they get better?

31:34.208 --> 31:35.833
They'll be making flying cars next.

31:35.916 --> 31:39.041
By the way, my name is Donatella.
She's Nadia.

31:39.125 --> 31:39.958
I'm Carlo.

31:40.041 --> 31:42.250
You'll have to give me directions.

31:42.333 --> 31:44.625
-I only know how to get to Colombo Street.
-Sure.

31:45.416 --> 31:46.708
What do you do? Do you work?

31:46.791 --> 31:48.708
No, I'm in my last year at school.

31:48.791 --> 31:51.333
Oh. How come you've got a car, then?

31:52.000 --> 31:53.625
It's my dad's, but I use it often.

31:54.291 --> 31:56.458
How about you?
What are you doing around here?

31:56.541 --> 31:57.833
We went to the movies.

31:57.916 --> 32:00.083
We saw <i>The Rocky Horror Picture Show.</i>

32:00.166 --> 32:02.416
-I haven't seen it yet.
-It's insane.

32:08.166 --> 32:09.625
Wasn't it screening in your area?

32:09.708 --> 32:12.916
What, is giving us a lift
that much trouble?

32:13.000 --> 32:15.458
No, of course not. I was just curious.

32:15.541 --> 32:16.833
-I'm just joking.
-All right.

32:16.916 --> 32:20.041
