32:34.416 --> 32:35.875
-Voilà.
-Very kind.

32:37.791 --> 32:40.250
-Can I put it on?
-Yes.

32:41.208 --> 32:43.000
-Do you like Battisti?
-I do.

33:16.500 --> 33:17.416
