35:46.083 --> 35:47.541
Good night, Giaele.

35:47.625 --> 35:50.125
Mom. And the prayer?

35:50.208 --> 35:51.083
Come on, say it.

35:51.583 --> 35:56.208
Dear Jesus, protect Lia, Mom, Dad,

35:56.291 --> 36:01.250
Gioacchino, Ezechiele and Elisabetta,

36:01.333 --> 36:03.666
Rachele, Tobia.

36:03.750 --> 36:05.583
Well done, my love.

36:06.250 --> 36:07.541
Very good. Now sleep.

36:20.583 --> 36:23.166
<i>Accepting an invitation could be risky.</i>

36:24.250 --> 36:26.958
<i>But if you turned it down,</i>
<i>you'd lose masculinity points.</i>

36:27.500 --> 36:29.208
<i>That's why I felt privileged</i>

36:29.291 --> 36:31.750
<i>to be invited to the Devil's Chair.</i>

36:33.666 --> 36:37.083
<i>The secret of our education</i>
<i>was to let the aggression out.</i>

36:37.583 --> 36:39.041
<i>Otherwise, it would build up.</i>

36:39.583 --> 36:41.416
<i>But without going too far,</i>

36:41.500 --> 36:43.750
<i>or we would have drifted into fascism.</i>

37:30.416 --> 37:32.458
Where were you?
We've been waiting for an hour.

37:32.541 --> 37:35.000
I met two girls. I gave them a lift home.

37:35.083 --> 37:36.416
Why didn't you bring them?

37:36.500 --> 37:38.291
They wanted a lift home.

37:38.375 --> 37:39.375
