37:39.458 --> 37:41.125
-They live far away.
-Where?

37:41.208 --> 37:42.166
In Montagnola.

37:43.625 --> 37:46.083
He ended up with some undesirables!

37:46.166 --> 37:47.666
So you went out whoring!

37:47.750 --> 37:49.500
You're the one who does that.

37:49.583 --> 37:51.583
I can deal with girls.

37:51.666 --> 37:54.833
Anyone would know how to deal with them.
They can't even speak.

37:54.916 --> 37:56.458
We don't want to talk to them.

37:56.541 --> 37:57.416
Introduce us.

37:58.291 --> 37:59.916
As if they'd give you their number!

38:00.000 --> 38:02.208
-What the fuck are you talking about?
-Look.

38:03.125 --> 38:05.583
-Here it is.
-Look here.

38:05.666 --> 38:07.375
-On my hand.
-On his little hand.

38:07.458 --> 38:10.333
-Let the master work.
-On his little hand.

38:10.416 --> 38:13.166
-Let the master work.
-On his hand.

38:13.250 --> 38:14.666
All right, then. Let's call them.

38:14.750 --> 38:15.916
Come on.

38:16.000 --> 38:18.625
-Go on, call your new friends.
-Come on.

38:18.708 --> 38:20.666
<i>We were the first generation to enjoy</i>

38:20.750 --> 38:23.125
<i>virtually limitless freedom.</i>

38:24.541 --> 38:26.083
<i>Our families seemed solid,</i>

38:26.166 --> 38:28.750
<i>but everything was</i>
<i>more fragile than it looked.</i>

38:28.833 --> 38:30.125
Edo!

38:30.666 --> 38:32.041
Can you help me with the test?

38:32.125 --> 38:33.416
No, Pik, don't…

38:33.500 --> 38:34.958
<i>Fathers were absent.</i>

38:35.041 --> 38:36.666
<i>Like Pik's father.</i>

38:36.750 --> 38:38.416
<i>No one had ever seen him.</i>

38:38.500 --> 38:40.083
<i>No one knew anything about him.</i>

38:40.750 --> 38:43.541
<i>But no one had the guts</i>
<i>to ask Pik where he was.</i>

38:52.000 --> 38:54.291
Shall we say three o'clock? Three thirty?

38:54.916 --> 38:55.875
