39:50.416 --> 39:52.208
Is that the way to ask for it?

39:52.708 --> 39:54.375
How am I supposed to ask?

39:56.833 --> 39:59.333
I don't know. Look at your friend Edoardo.

40:00.166 --> 40:02.750
Does he look like someone
who asks his mom for everything?

40:09.625 --> 40:10.750
I will never make it.

40:12.666 --> 40:14.625
