41:48.250 --> 41:50.208
Because they have an exoskeleton,

41:50.291 --> 41:51.666
which is hard,

41:51.750 --> 41:53.583
but at the same time flexible.

41:55.666 --> 41:57.375
It's a body that can mutate.

41:57.458 --> 41:58.458
Change.

41:59.375 --> 42:02.000
And everything
that causes change is violent.

42:03.625 --> 42:07.166
Violent changes destroy,
but also create at the same time.

42:08.458 --> 42:09.541
See?

42:10.375 --> 42:12.041
I should kill him exactly here,

42:12.125 --> 42:14.208
just here, in the chest.

42:15.250 --> 42:16.833
Then yes, he would die.

42:18.000 --> 42:19.708
That would be the easiest way.

42:20.833 --> 42:22.083
It's the same with people.

42:24.333 --> 42:27.750
It's pointless to waste time
looking for a way to kill a man.

42:28.625 --> 42:30.416
There's no need to overthink it.

42:33.291 --> 42:34.125
