43:37.666 --> 43:39.041
<i>It became clear to me</i>

43:39.125 --> 43:42.708
<i>that the madness of one family member</i>
<i>ended in another one's quirks.</i>

43:44.125 --> 43:45.750
<i>Arbus wasn't a violent guy.</i>

43:46.666 --> 43:48.500
<i>Yet he was obsessed with death.</i>

43:50.375 --> 43:52.625
<i>If even Arbus' family</i>
<i>was attracted to evil,</i>

43:52.708 --> 43:54.875
<i>perhaps Professor Golgota was right.</i>

43:54.958 --> 43:57.958
<i>Maybe, in order to become men,</i>
<i>it was necessary to experience evil.</i>

44:00.833 --> 44:01.708
Hi there.

44:02.416 --> 44:03.708
-Hi.
-Remember me? Monica.

44:03.791 --> 44:06.583
We met last summer at the Circeo.

44:07.125 --> 44:08.541
Oh, yeah, Monica. Sorry.

44:09.125 --> 44:09.958
What are you doing?

44:10.041 --> 44:11.458
Well, I was going home.

44:11.541 --> 44:13.416
You never called me back.

44:13.500 --> 44:15.541
Because I'd lost your number,
so I couldn't…

44:15.625 --> 44:17.166
It's okay, I'll give it to you again.

44:18.333 --> 44:20.916
Let me write it here,
so you won't lose it again.

44:34.500 --> 44:35.333
Bye.

44:35.833 --> 44:36.666
Bye.

44:41.916 --> 44:43.958
<i>Even if none of us would have admitted it,</i>

44:44.041 --> 44:46.416
<i>we were all deeply scared of sex.</i>

44:48.000 --> 44:50.083
<i>It was a mystery that had to be unveiled.</i>

44:50.166 --> 44:52.500
<i>We were attracted to it</i>
<i>without knowing why.</i>

44:53.666 --> 44:55.500
<i>Some used it to achieve freedom.</i>

44:57.083 --> 44:58.708
<i>Others used it to destroy.</i>

44:59.208 --> 45:02.791
Mom, this is one of my schoolmates.
Stefano Jervi.

45:05.625 --> 45:06.833
Good evening, ma'am.

45:06.916 --> 45:07.958
Bye, Mom.

45:08.041 --> 45:09.375
Didn't you get him a present?

45:09.458 --> 45:11.958
-D'Avenia and I got one together.
-What did you get him?

45:17.500 --> 45:18.333
Benazza!

45:19.208 --> 45:20.208
How's it going?

