1:07:23.958 --> 1:07:25.625
There he is. I'll go say hi.

1:07:34.041 --> 1:07:35.458
Leda, what's happened?

1:07:36.875 --> 1:07:38.833
-Can I do anything?
-Don't get involved.

1:07:40.541 --> 1:07:42.583
Look at you. You're a child.

1:08:11.000 --> 1:08:13.333
Carlo must have gone for a swim.
Come with me.

1:08:16.500 --> 1:08:17.375
Please.

1:08:18.166 --> 1:08:20.375
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

1:08:26.708 --> 1:08:29.500
Wait. I'll just park the car. One second.

1:08:50.583 --> 1:08:51.750
Gosh.

1:08:53.833 --> 1:08:55.666
I've never seen a house like this.

1:09:00.833 --> 1:09:02.291
Hello, good morning.

1:09:02.375 --> 1:09:03.875
May I speak to Monica?

1:09:03.958 --> 1:09:05.000
<i>Speaking.</i>

1:09:05.083 --> 1:09:05.958
Good morning, miss.

1:09:06.041 --> 1:09:07.750
This is Dr. Edoardo Albinati's assistant.

1:09:07.833 --> 1:09:09.333
You know who I'm talking about?

1:09:09.416 --> 1:09:12.291
Mr. Albinati would like
to invite you to a party at Circeo.

1:09:12.375 --> 1:09:15.000
He thought it would be a nice idea,
since you first met there.

1:09:15.083 --> 1:09:16.750
Can you confirm?

1:09:16.833 --> 1:09:18.875
<i>-But is Edoardo there?</i>
-Say yes.

1:09:18.958 --> 1:09:20.541
Yes. I'll put him on now.

1:09:20.625 --> 1:09:23.750
We are now forwarding your call
to Mr. Edoardo Albinati.

1:09:26.250 --> 1:09:27.250
Hi, Monica.

1:09:27.333 --> 1:09:28.333
<i>Who was that?</i>

1:09:28.416 --> 1:09:29.833
A friend of mine.

1:09:29.916 --> 1:09:31.208
<i>Funny guy.</i>

1:09:31.291 --> 1:09:32.791
Well, at least it worked.

1:09:32.875 --> 1:09:33.708
<i>How so?</i>

1:09:34.208 --> 1:09:37.083
Well, you and I
are going on a date, aren't we?

1:09:37.916 --> 1:09:39.666
I'm here with my assistant.

1:09:40.833 --> 1:09:42.458
<i>Okay. What's the plan?</i>

1:09:42.541 --> 1:09:45.083
-Shall we come pick you up in an hour?
-Yes.

1:09:46.416 --> 1:09:48.416
-You definitely have your car?
-Of course.

1:09:48.500 --> 1:09:49.458
Pik…

1:09:50.416 --> 1:09:51.333
Pik.

1:09:51.416 --> 1:09:53.125
Please, behave.

1:09:53.708 --> 1:09:55.333
-Yes, sorry.
-No bullshit.

1:11:19.708 --> 1:11:20.958
We're early.

1:11:21.041 --> 1:11:23.583
Why don't we go to my house
before heading to the party?

1:11:53.125 --> 1:11:54.708
This house is amazing.

1:11:54.791 --> 1:11:55.625
Yeah.

1:11:56.791 --> 1:11:57.875
-Thanks.
-You're welcome.

1:12:02.500 --> 1:12:03.875
-Cheers.
-To you.

1:12:11.541 --> 1:12:13.500
You're really amazing.

1:12:22.416 --> 1:12:23.666
I'm not thinking straight.

1:12:33.458 --> 1:12:34.541
Edo?

1:12:40.750 --> 1:12:43.333
I've never been with a girl.

1:12:45.333 --> 1:12:46.708
Have you seen Erika?

1:12:47.875 --> 1:12:49.875
How she looks at me? How she touches me?

1:12:49.958 --> 1:12:51.250
Please.

1:12:51.333 --> 1:12:52.750
Don't touch me.

1:12:52.833 --> 1:12:55.041
-She thinks you're funny.
-Come on.

1:12:55.541 --> 1:12:56.958
-Yeah? Is that it?
-Yes.

1:12:57.041 --> 1:12:58.375
Come on, Pik, please.

1:12:58.458 --> 1:13:00.041
-You're annoying.
-And then?

1:13:00.125 --> 1:13:01.000
That's it.

1:13:01.083 --> 1:13:02.875
That's more than enough.

1:13:02.958 --> 1:13:04.291
Is that more than enough?

1:13:05.083 --> 1:13:06.208
Don't kid me.

1:13:06.916 --> 1:13:08.166
I know there's more.

1:13:08.250 --> 1:13:09.833
-Come on.
-There's nothing more.

1:13:09.916 --> 1:13:11.625
Chill out, please.

1:13:13.125 --> 1:13:15.000
-What shall I do?
-Don't do anything.

1:13:15.958 --> 1:13:17.333
Nothing, Pik, okay?

1:13:18.166 --> 1:13:19.583
Don't do anything.

1:13:27.750 --> 1:13:29.291
We'll see.

1:13:31.333 --> 1:13:32.666
What do we do now?

1:13:35.208 --> 1:13:36.208
Come on.

1:13:37.125 --> 1:13:38.166
Come on.

1:14:06.041 --> 1:14:08.083
Wait, not like that. Wait.

1:14:09.166 --> 1:14:10.208
Wait.

1:14:13.416 --> 1:14:14.416
Monica.

1:14:17.416 --> 1:14:19.500
You are completely crazy.

1:14:21.333 --> 1:14:22.458
It's time to go.

1:14:23.500 --> 1:14:24.833
What's happened?

1:14:25.708 --> 1:14:26.708
I have to go home.

1:14:27.333 --> 1:14:29.458
I couldn't do it. I want to go home.

1:14:29.541 --> 1:14:31.250
Pik! Where are you going?

1:14:36.208 --> 1:14:37.416
I'm sorry.

1:14:39.000 --> 1:14:42.125
<i>That summer, we understood</i>
<i>that we couldn't erase our mistakes,</i>

1:14:42.208 --> 1:14:45.333
<i>because they were embedded in our school,</i>
<i>inside our homes.</i>

1:14:46.416 --> 1:14:49.000
<i>They were right before our eyes,</i>
<i>but no one could see them.</i>

1:14:49.083 --> 1:14:50.791
<i>No one had the courage to talk about it.</i>

1:14:52.500 --> 1:14:55.333
<i>We had a mask of innocence</i>
<i>stitched on our faces.</i>

1:14:56.041 --> 1:14:57.333
<i>But, suddenly, at that time,</i>

1:14:57.416 --> 1:15:00.250
<i>there was no distinction</i>
<i>between a bunch of reckless kids</i>

1:15:00.333 --> 1:15:01.458
<i>and ferocious murderers.</i>

1:15:01.541 --> 1:15:02.625
It's getting late.

1:15:04.583 --> 1:15:07.083
Sorry, when is Carlo coming?

1:15:07.166 --> 1:15:08.375
Are you not having fun?

1:15:08.458 --> 1:15:11.458
-Yes, but we should be heading home soon.
-Yeah.

1:15:17.458 --> 1:15:18.708
For now, you're staying.

1:15:20.916 --> 1:15:22.625
What, are you playing now?

1:15:24.000 --> 1:15:25.708
What's going on?

1:15:27.291 --> 1:15:28.958
-Come with me.
-No.

1:15:29.041 --> 1:15:30.375
-Come with me!
-Go.

1:15:31.458 --> 1:15:32.416
Come on.

1:15:33.250 --> 1:15:34.166
Up the stairs!

1:15:37.083 --> 1:15:38.791
-You dirty…
-In the toilet!

1:15:44.000 --> 1:15:45.000
What do you want from us?

1:15:48.916 --> 1:15:50.083
Get off me!

1:15:52.250 --> 1:15:53.833
If you scream, I'll beat you up.

1:15:57.291 --> 1:15:58.208
Open up!

1:15:59.041 --> 1:16:00.791
Open up, please!

1:16:04.541 --> 1:16:05.666
I have to go home.

1:16:06.291 --> 1:16:07.666
Come back soon, okay?

1:16:10.875 --> 1:16:12.666
Remember to call my parents.

1:16:12.750 --> 1:16:13.750
Open up!

1:16:16.375 --> 1:16:19.208
Open up!

1:16:19.291 --> 1:16:21.541
-I want to go home!
-Let us go, please.

1:16:21.625 --> 1:16:22.458
I want to--

1:17:06.750 --> 1:17:08.375
I'm sorry about the other night.

1:17:09.125 --> 1:17:10.125
About my brother.

1:17:11.541 --> 1:17:13.625
I just wanted to apologize.

1:18:06.500 --> 1:18:09.166
Sorry, I got a flat tire.
I had no way of letting you know.

1:18:10.708 --> 1:18:11.666
Sit down.

1:18:12.333 --> 1:18:13.916
Can I make a call?

1:18:15.333 --> 1:18:17.041
-Make it quick.
-Thanks.

1:18:28.500 --> 1:18:30.125
Hello, ma'am, Guido speaking.

1:18:30.208 --> 1:18:32.375
Listen, I wanted to tell you

1:18:32.458 --> 1:18:35.083
that Angelo asked me to tell you
that he won't be home tonight.

1:18:35.166 --> 1:18:37.166
The other entrepreneurs aren't stupid.

1:18:37.875 --> 1:18:39.458
Yes, he's with Gianluca, yes.

1:18:40.041 --> 1:18:42.583
They're going to the American flea market
tomorrow morning.

1:18:44.333 --> 1:18:45.500
Thanks. Bye.

1:18:52.250 --> 1:18:54.791
But in the long run,
it could turn out to be a boomerang.

1:18:55.375 --> 1:18:56.375
For the country.

1:18:56.458 --> 1:18:58.333
It's the safest way to invest.

1:18:58.416 --> 1:19:00.291
Sure, interest rates are low, but…

1:19:01.208 --> 1:19:02.833
I know. I do know.

1:19:04.416 --> 1:19:06.083
Then tell him. Convince him.

1:19:07.541 --> 1:19:09.083
It's for our children too.

1:19:10.875 --> 1:19:12.250
It's their money too.

1:19:13.708 --> 1:19:14.541
Sure.

1:19:16.541 --> 1:19:17.541
What's wrong?

1:19:18.291 --> 1:19:19.250
Aren't you hungry?

1:20:15.250 --> 1:20:16.500
Where are you taking me?

1:20:17.250 --> 1:20:18.333
Donatella!

1:21:03.375 --> 1:21:04.208
Your turn.

1:21:07.416 --> 1:21:09.250
Come on. Come.

1:21:11.291 --> 1:21:12.291
Come on!

1:21:13.833 --> 1:21:15.208
Yes. Good girl.

1:21:15.833 --> 1:21:17.833
Come on. Don't be afraid.

1:21:50.916 --> 1:21:51.875
Strip.

1:21:53.375 --> 1:21:54.500
Come on.

1:21:54.583 --> 1:21:55.791
Strip.

1:21:57.000 --> 1:21:58.041
Good girl.

1:22:06.125 --> 1:22:07.333
Then will you let us go?

1:22:07.416 --> 1:22:08.416
Yes, of course.

1:22:13.208 --> 1:22:15.208
We've never been home so late.

1:22:16.208 --> 1:22:18.125
What are we going to tell our parents?

1:22:20.958 --> 1:22:21.916
Hurry up.

1:22:25.708 --> 1:22:28.083
Please, take us home,
or they'll be worried.

1:22:28.166 --> 1:22:29.166
Come on.

1:22:33.750 --> 1:22:35.208
We won't say anything.

1:22:35.750 --> 1:22:36.875
Everything off.

1:22:38.000 --> 1:22:39.083
No, please.

1:22:42.083 --> 1:22:43.125
I beg you.

1:22:45.458 --> 1:22:47.125
Come on. Then we'll see.

1:23:30.250 --> 1:23:31.291
Donatella.

1:23:32.500 --> 1:23:33.666
Did you hear that?

1:23:33.750 --> 1:23:35.333
-What?
-There's a car.

1:23:36.083 --> 1:23:37.458
Help!

1:23:37.541 --> 1:23:39.958
-We've been locked up!
-Open up!

1:23:40.041 --> 1:23:40.916
Help, please!

1:23:43.500 --> 1:23:44.791
Help!

1:23:44.875 --> 1:23:46.291
-Please, help us!
-Help!

1:23:46.375 --> 1:23:47.750
-Help us!
-Open up!

1:23:47.833 --> 1:23:49.041
Help!

1:23:52.583 --> 1:23:53.833
What the fuck are you doing?

1:23:54.583 --> 1:23:55.708
I'll beat you up!

1:23:55.791 --> 1:23:57.416
-Got it?
-Okay!

1:23:58.000 --> 1:23:59.625
We kept Bulgari locked up here.

1:23:59.708 --> 1:24:01.208
You think we'd let you screw us?

1:24:01.291 --> 1:24:02.125
-No!
-Stop it!

1:24:02.208 --> 1:24:03.166
Shut up!

1:24:03.250 --> 1:24:04.583
Jacques will be here soon.

1:24:05.708 --> 1:24:07.750
The Marsigliesi boss.
He told us to kidnap you.

1:24:07.833 --> 1:24:09.416
-This is his place.
-Stop it!

1:24:12.750 --> 1:24:13.833
Come on.

1:24:22.916 --> 1:24:24.375
I want to go home.

1:24:25.666 --> 1:24:26.958
I want to go home.

1:24:27.041 --> 1:24:28.875
Fuck, I'm done with these two.

1:24:28.958 --> 1:24:30.250
I'll go get Andrea.

1:25:08.625 --> 1:25:09.625
This is Jacques.

1:25:10.958 --> 1:25:11.791
Hi.

1:25:13.916 --> 1:25:14.958
Hey, say hi.

1:25:15.041 --> 1:25:15.958
Angelo!

1:25:16.875 --> 1:25:19.125
You shouldn't beat her like that.

1:25:20.875 --> 1:25:21.875
Right?

1:25:23.166 --> 1:25:24.208
Hey.

1:25:25.708 --> 1:25:26.708
Hi.

1:25:30.666 --> 1:25:32.541
Jacques, don't force me to sleep with you.

1:25:32.625 --> 1:25:34.250
We can't take it anymore.

1:25:36.625 --> 1:25:37.750
Don't worry.

1:25:38.583 --> 1:25:40.541
If you don't want to, I won't force you.

1:25:44.416 --> 1:25:45.583
Take us back home.

1:25:46.333 --> 1:25:47.541
Please.

1:25:51.083 --> 1:25:52.041
Please.

1:25:54.708 --> 1:25:56.791
We'll find a way to get you home, okay?

1:25:58.791 --> 1:25:59.916
Okay?

1:26:01.250 --> 1:26:04.250
As long as you don't tell anyone
about what happened here.

1:26:05.291 --> 1:26:06.125
Yes?

1:26:06.791 --> 1:26:08.083
Yes?

1:26:08.166 --> 1:26:09.500
-Is that clear?
-I swear.

1:26:09.583 --> 1:26:10.583
Good.

1:26:12.791 --> 1:26:13.791
And you?

1:26:16.375 --> 1:26:17.208
Hey.

1:26:17.791 --> 1:26:20.416
Wanna come with me?
Come on, don't be afraid.

1:26:29.958 --> 1:26:30.958
Come on.

1:26:34.125 --> 1:26:35.125
Come on.

1:26:36.625 --> 1:26:38.583
Let's go.

1:26:50.708 --> 1:26:51.833
No, please.

1:26:51.916 --> 1:26:53.708
No, don't worry.

1:26:54.791 --> 1:26:55.916
Let me go, please.

1:26:58.333 --> 1:26:59.291
No.

1:27:18.166 --> 1:27:19.375
What is it?

1:27:19.458 --> 1:27:20.875
It'll put you to sleep.

1:27:20.958 --> 1:27:22.166
No. Please, no.

1:27:22.250 --> 1:27:24.500
-Please.
-Don't move. You'll make it worse.

1:27:24.583 --> 1:27:25.416
Don't move.

1:27:30.375 --> 1:27:31.583
Was that so difficult?

1:27:34.458 --> 1:27:36.416
These two are useless now.

1:27:37.208 --> 1:27:39.291
They've always been useless.

1:27:39.375 --> 1:27:40.625
That's not true.

1:27:41.958 --> 1:27:43.208
I don't even fancy them.

1:27:43.708 --> 1:27:44.958
Who, these two?

1:27:48.208 --> 1:27:50.416
This stuff doesn't work.
She's not passing out.

1:27:50.916 --> 1:27:52.916
-Have you tried with the pillow?
-No.

1:27:53.708 --> 1:27:55.375
I have this. What do you think?

1:27:57.333 --> 1:27:58.583
-Come on, now.
-No.

1:27:58.666 --> 1:28:00.041
Move!

1:28:30.208 --> 1:28:31.833
What are they doing to her?

1:28:31.916 --> 1:28:33.541
Do something, please.

1:28:35.833 --> 1:28:36.958
Please.

1:28:40.083 --> 1:28:41.750
-Shall I go?
-Yes, you go.

1:28:43.291 --> 1:28:45.750
-Give me your arm.
-Stop.

1:28:45.833 --> 1:28:47.416
-Here we go.
-Stop.

1:29:10.458 --> 1:29:12.250
Look what your friend did to me.

1:29:12.333 --> 1:29:14.000
Here. And here.

1:29:18.958 --> 1:29:20.166
That's enough.

1:29:20.708 --> 1:29:23.875
If you can't fall asleep,
I'll have to use a karate move.

1:29:24.666 --> 1:29:25.791
No, please.

1:29:27.666 --> 1:29:29.041
Yes, actually.

1:29:29.750 --> 1:29:31.916
I'm all out of patience with you.

1:29:34.583 --> 1:29:36.666
Tell me if you prefer a karate move

1:29:36.750 --> 1:29:39.208
or a blow with the gun's grip
behind your head.

1:29:42.958 --> 1:29:45.541
Do you prefer a karate move

1:29:45.625 --> 1:29:48.541
or a blow with the gun's grip
behind your head?

1:29:51.250 --> 1:29:52.416
A karate move.

1:29:53.791 --> 1:29:55.166
A karate move.

1:29:55.250 --> 1:29:57.625
A karate move!

1:31:03.875 --> 1:31:04.833
Hello?

1:31:04.916 --> 1:31:06.458
-They're killing me.
-Bitch!

1:31:06.541 --> 1:31:08.250
Please!

1:31:11.375 --> 1:31:13.333
You don't get it!

1:31:21.333 --> 1:31:23.333
Can we put them in the trunk?

1:31:23.916 --> 1:31:24.916
Okay.

1:31:25.958 --> 1:31:27.041
Come on, then.

1:31:29.083 --> 1:31:30.708
You have to use a blanket.

1:32:01.000 --> 1:32:03.000
This one took her time to die.

1:32:28.625 --> 1:32:29.541
Andrea.

1:32:30.125 --> 1:32:32.041
I told you not to call me that.

1:32:42.083 --> 1:32:43.791
What are we going to do with them?

1:32:44.333 --> 1:32:45.416
I don't know.

1:32:46.166 --> 1:32:49.041
You deal with them.
I have to take care of the house.

1:32:51.833 --> 1:32:52.958
I'll make a call.

1:32:53.541 --> 1:32:55.791
I'll ask Gianluca to tell our parents.

1:33:00.166 --> 1:33:02.291
Look how well they're sleeping.

1:33:14.416 --> 1:33:16.791
<i>Yes, I get it, Gianluca,</i>
<i>but where is my son?</i>

1:33:18.583 --> 1:33:19.500
At Angelo's?

1:33:20.041 --> 1:33:22.250
He said he was going to Maurizio's place.

1:33:24.333 --> 1:33:25.750
At the last minute.

1:33:26.666 --> 1:33:27.958
Yes, yes, that's fine.

1:33:28.041 --> 1:33:29.041
Thanks.

1:33:35.500 --> 1:33:36.416
Who was that?

1:33:37.166 --> 1:33:38.208
Gianluca.

1:33:38.833 --> 1:33:40.750
They're coming back. Everything is okay.

1:33:40.833 --> 1:33:42.458
I told you, didn't I?

1:33:54.708 --> 1:33:57.666
They were pieces of meat,
and they still are pieces of meat.

1:34:02.791 --> 1:34:05.208
Only our friendship can save us.

1:34:06.250 --> 1:34:08.291
Only our brotherhood.

1:34:11.458 --> 1:34:14.541
Friends of death, friends in death.

1:34:15.541 --> 1:34:19.166
Friends of death, friends in death.

1:34:19.250 --> 1:34:23.666
Friends of death, friends in death! Fuck.

1:34:26.166 --> 1:34:27.833
What time are the others coming?

1:34:27.916 --> 1:34:28.750
In an hour.

1:34:28.833 --> 1:34:30.375
Let's have pizza.

1:34:30.458 --> 1:34:32.000
I can't. I gotta go home.

1:34:32.083 --> 1:34:35.125
Home? What am I supposed to do
here alone for an hour?

1:34:35.208 --> 1:34:37.583
No idea, Angelo.
I'm gonna see you later anyway.

1:34:38.125 --> 1:34:40.125
We can do it when no one sees us.

1:34:50.208 --> 1:34:51.583
Okay, but what time?

1:34:52.208 --> 1:34:53.708
At three. Okay?

1:34:55.750 --> 1:34:56.583
Angelo, here.

1:34:56.666 --> 1:34:58.583
These are the keys to the car

1:34:58.666 --> 1:34:59.791
and to the gate.

1:34:59.875 --> 1:35:02.208
So you can get in
without making any noise. Okay?

1:35:02.708 --> 1:35:03.833
I'll see you later.

1:36:01.458 --> 1:36:02.458
Rosa'.

1:36:06.958 --> 1:36:07.958
Rosaria.

1:36:11.166 --> 1:36:12.458
They've left.

1:36:16.458 --> 1:36:17.458
Rosaria.

